msgid "Regenerate API key"
msgstr "Znovu vygenerovať API kľúč"

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:730
msgid ""
"Leave enabled to revoke the current API key and generate a new one. This is "
"recommended if you suspect your password was compromised. Disable it to keep "
"your current API key active after changing your password."
msgstr ""
"Nechajte povolené na zrušenie aktuálneho API kľúča a vygenerovanie nového. "
"Odporúča sa, ak máte podozrenie, že vaše heslo bolo kompromitované. Zakážte "
"to, aby ste si ponechali aktuálny API kľúč aktívny po zmene hesla."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:766
msgid "Your password has been changed."
msgstr "Vaše heslo bolo zmenené."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:780
msgid "Current password"
msgstr "Aktuálne heslo"

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:781
msgid "Leave empty if you have not set a password yet."
msgstr "Nechajte prázdne, ak ste ešte nenastavili heslo."

